      <prop type="x-translation-ref">桑扈.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>交交桑扈，有鶯其羽。君子樂胥，受天之祜。
交交桑扈，有鶯其領。君子樂胥，萬邦之屏。
之屏之翰，百辟為憲。不戢不難，受福不那。
兕觥其觩，旨酒思柔。彼交匪敖，萬福來求。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>They flit about, the greenbeaks,
With their
​variegated wings.
To be rejoiced in are these princes!
May they receive the blessing of Heaven!</seg>
      </tuv>
